data.description: Check out the elegance of this spacious 4-bedroom home in the great subdivision "Autumn Canyon" neighborhood. With high ceilings and laminate flooring throughout, this open plan gem has a perfect blend of space and style. The finished basement adds an extra touch of coziness and extra space for a man cave or extra space for a growing teenager or visitors. Located within the renowned Cartersville City School District, convenience is at your doorstep. The flow between the living Room, dining area, and kitchen creates a seamless living experience. The kitchen has gently used wood cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a generous pantry. The backyard is spacious and leveled, also privacy-fenced added. Don't miss out on this remarkable opportunity.   Schedule a showing through showing time, using the Supra Lockbox. Community amenities include sidewalks, a playground, and a covered pavilion. Has new roof and a storage shed.
